title: Tilt 2 Win E-Sports Looking for new Toplaner around Platinum
body:
We looking for a Toplaner that is able to work with low resources and is able to play tank toplaner and also some kind of carry toplaner.
Toxicity isn't welcome even when the teamname is "Tilt 2 Win"
Decent shotcalling and game knowledge is needed
Fast shotcalling hard recommended

Write me on my email: bolleklolbusiness@gmail.com  or add me in league: T2W Bollek
